{
  "name": "Hinderance: Phobic",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/death/skull-humanoid-white-red.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have a crippling phobia. Choose one phobia, such as acrophobia (heights), agoraphobia (open spaces), arachnophobia (spiders), astraphobia (storms), coulrophobia (clowns), cynophobia (dogs), ophidiophobia (snakes), or any other phobia which could come into play in an adventure. <strong>When exposed to the trigger for your phobia, you are frightened until you are no longer exposed to the trigger.</strong></p><p>One of your ability scores of your choice increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>",
